optical-fingerprints-inside-materials-without-lasers</guid></item><item><title>光子学的进步可以实现紧凑、高性能的激光雷达传感器</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/photonics-advance-could-enable-compact-high-performance-lidar-sensors</link><description>激光雷达系统使用红外光脉冲来测量距离并绘制高分辨率的 3D 场景图，使自动驾驶车辆能够对其路径中出现的障碍物快速做出反应。但传统的激光雷达传感器是昂贵、笨重的系统，有许多移动部件，这些部件会随着时间的推移而退化，限制了传感器的部署方式。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/photonics-advance-could-enable-compact-high-performance-lidar-sensors.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 May 2026 12:21:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/photonics-advance-could-enable-compact-high-performance-lidar-sensors</guid></item><item><title>团队在石墨烯中引导电子自旋弹道</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/team-steers-electron-spin-ballistically-in-graphene</link><description>曼彻斯特大学国家石墨烯研究所的研究人员表明，超洁净石墨烯中的电子可以高精度地操纵，同时保持其自旋信息完整，这是未来低功耗电子和量子设备的关键要求。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/team-steers-electron-spin-ballistically-in-graphene.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 May 2026 12:06:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/team-steers-electron-spin-ballistically-in-graphene</guid></item><item><title>外太阳系的这个小世界应该没有空气，但它有大气层</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/this-tiny-world-in-the-outer-solar-system-should-be-airless-but-it-has-an-atmosphere</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 May 2026 11:51:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/this-tiny-world-in-the-outer-solar-system-should-be-airless-but-it-has-an-atmosphere</guid></item><item><title>PCPJack 凭证窃取者利用 5 个 CVE 在云系统中像蠕虫一样传播</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/pcpjack-credential-stealer-exploits-5-cves-to-spread-worm-like-across-cloud-systems</link><description>PCPJack 通过 6 个 Python 模块利用 5 个 CVE 窃取凭证，从而实现云传播和欺诈驱动的攻击。 &lt;img src="https:/